  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dbb\u0dda \u0db4\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0db8\u0db1\u0da7 \u0d9a\u0db3\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0dd4\u0d9c\u0dd1\u0dc3\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Tear gas on the march",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police fired tear gas and water cannons to disperse the march organized jointly by the Inter-University Student Union, trade unions and mass organizations.",
        "The march that started from near the Maradana Elphinstone Theater and moved towards the Technical Intersection was deployed in the vicinity of the police, anti-riot units and water cannons to disperse the march at the Technical Intersection, but the protestors changed course and moved towards the Colombo City Hall, and then the Ministry of Defense and Health. They fired tear gas and water cannons nearby to disperse the protestors.",
        "Amidst tear gas and water cannons, the protestors again moved towards the technical intersection, and the police and anti-riot units were also seen chasing them and working to disperse the protest.",
        "This protest was organized by forcing the government to stop the repression carried out by using the Prevention of Terrorism Act and to release the arrested activists of the struggle."
      ],
